title: CHARNETT MOFFETT / Net Man / Blue Note / 1987
description:
Charles Moffett, drummer with Ornette Coleman; named his son after himself and 

Ornette.....(CHAR)les  or(NETT)e.   The final E was lost in creation apparently.

At the age of 20, Charnett recorded NET MAN; his first effort as leader.  I

bought this years ago on a whim and have been enjoying it several times a year

ever since.  Nice grooves are set and embellished upon.  It just might grab you 

too.
